snippet.title: Secret Game -Killer Queen- Portable OP
snippet.description:
NO MORE GAME - 遊女

The PSP version is set for release on May. 27th, 2010. It will contain extra features as well as the BET system from the PS2 release.

http://www.yetigame.jp/secretgame_psp/index.html
